## Troubleshooting

### pgvector not available

```bash
# Install pgvector extension
brew install pgvector  # macOS
# OR
apt-get install postgresql-15-pgvector  # Linux
```

### Low retrieval quality

1. Check chunk size (try 1000-1500 tokens)
2. Increase overlap (200-300 tokens)
3. Enable reranking
4. Use hybrid search for specific keywords

### High token costs

1. Use smaller embedding models
2. Reduce chunk count retrieved
3. Implement caching for common queries
4. Use cheaper generation models for simple queries

